  id: Ship in a bottle
  displayName: Ship in a bottle
  introText: You find a ship in a bottle floating through space. The ship inside
    looks exactly like your own and whispers to you "set me free". It also seems
    to follow the movement of the astral sea a moment ahead of your ship.
  choices:
  - choiceText: Keep the ship in the bottle
    outcomeText: Monitoring the bottle allows you to get early warnings about incoming
      damage.
